snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get Together: Rule The Dance Floor Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn all new DJ & Dancing skills in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack and rule the dance floor!
 
Learn More: http://o.ea.com/47812
 
Create and join clubs, get together with other Sims for exciting group activities, and live it up in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack, available this December!
